snippet.title: The Occupation - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Website: http://occupation-game.com
Company Website: http://whitepapergames.com/
Twitter: @WhitePaperGames

The Occupation is a politically driven, first-person, narrative game set in 1980’s North-West England in which you play as a whistleblowing journalist.
